   a) functional programming
   b) oop programming

Programming Language Type:
   a) Compiled Languages
        C/C++/Java/C#
        -Game/hardware controller (speed)
   b) Interpredted Languages
         PHP,Python,JavaScript
         -data analysis/visualization/AI(slow)


